heaviest_rainfall.status: Ranked 7th for total rainfall, today's storm had precipitation totalling 23.86mm, falling at 8.3mm per hour at times during the 31.0 hour long storm.  47.89mm of rain was recorded as having fallen on 09 November 2025, marking an exceptional 144.8 hour precipitation event. heaviest_rainrate.status: The rain rate reached 34.3mm per hour on 02 September 2025, and resulted in 21.19mm of rain over 15.0 hours.  This is the highest rate recorded by our weather station.

longest_rain.status: Today, one rain storm lasted for 31.0 hours (ranking 7th for longest storm from our records).  It accumulated 23.86mm of rain and it fell at 8.3mm per hour at times.
